Package rql4j.builder Description

This package contains the classes to create the rql-statement. All classes extend the abstract class RqlBuilder which contains the execute method. The execute method is used by the RqlCommand to execute the rql-statement and store the result. RqlBuilder cotains inner classes which represent the action which should perform.

The classes to build the rql-statement have a analogy to the official rql documentation. The builder to create a rql-statement to list all categories of a project for example is CategoriesBuilder.List.
